# AudioFlam .clinerules

## Tech Stack
- **Framework:** SvelteKit 2 + Svelte 5 (TypeScript, strict mode)
- **Hosting:** Cloudflare Pages (adapter-cloudflare)
- **Styling:** Native CSS variables (no Tailwind)
- **Video Export:** WebCodecs API (H.264/MP4) + MediaRecorder fallback + api.video cloud transcoding
- **Transcription:** Whisper via @huggingface/transformers (Web Worker)
- **Audio Processing:** SoundTouchJS (time-stretching), lamejs (MP3), Mediabunny (MP4 muxing)

## Key Conventions
- **Svelte 5 Runes:** Use `$state`, `$effect`, `$derived` (not reactive declarations)
- **TypeScript:** Strict mode enabled; avoid unchecked type assertions
- **CSS:** All styling via `src/app.css` CSS variables; no inline styles
- **Stores:** Centralized in `src/lib/stores.ts` (writable + custom)
- **API Routes:** `src/routes/api/*/+server.ts` (SvelteKit server endpoints)
- **Utilities:** `src/lib/utils/*.ts` (pure functions, no side effects)
- **Components:** `src/lib/components/*.svelte` (single responsibility)
- **Logging:** Use prefixes `[WebCodecs]`, `[VideoExport]`, `[TTS]`, `[Transcription]` for console logs

## APIs & Services
- **Azure Speech TTS:** `env.AZURE_SPEECH_KEY`, `env.AZURE_SPEECH_REGION` (fast, ~3s)
- **YarnGPT TTS:** `env.YARNGPT_API_KEY` (native Nigerian voices, ~30s)
- **api.video:** `env.APIVIDEO_API_KEY` (cloud transcoding, WebM → MP4)
- **Hugging Face Transformers:** Whisper model (quantized or full, 100-350MB)

## What NOT to Do
- ❌ **No authentication** - Public, educational use only
- ❌ **No Tailwind** - CSS variables only
- ❌ **No audio playback during WebCodecs export** - Causes stuttering; use pre-computed FFT frames
- ❌ **Don't assume MediaRecorder H.264 works on Android** - Always check WebCodecs first
- ❌ **Don't forget XML escaping in SSML** - User text must be escaped before embedding
- ❌ **Don't use Buffer.from() in Cloudflare** - Use `btoa()` for base64 encoding
- ❌ **Don't add heavy dependencies** - Keep bundle <500KB
- ❌ **Don't break robots.txt** - Must remain `noindex, nofollow` (educational use)
- ❌ **Don't play audio during export** - Render with pre-computed FFT data instead
- ❌ **Don't forget mono→stereo conversion** - AAC encoders reject mono audio

