## File Navigation (Quick Reference)
- **TTS:** `src/routes/api/tts/+server.ts` + `src/routes/+page.svelte`
- **Audiogram:** `src/lib/components/AudiogramPage.svelte` + `src/lib/utils/compositor.ts`
- **Export:** `src/lib/utils/video-export.ts` (orchestration)
- **Transcription:** `src/lib/components/TranscribePage.svelte` + `src/lib/utils/transcription.ts`
- **Waveform:** `src/lib/utils/waveform.ts` (precomputeFrequencyFrames critical)
- **Audio Processing:** `src/lib/audioProcessing.ts` + `src/lib/server/silenceRemoval.ts`
- **Design:** `src/app.css` (CSS variables)

## Critical Patterns
- **Waveform Export Parity:** Use `precomputeFrequencyFrames()` before export; pass pre-computed frames to `renderFrame(currentTime)`
- **Two-Speaker Mode:** Call `concatenateAudioSegments()` after generating both voices
- **Transcription:** Run in Web Worker via `getWorker()`; call `releaseModel()` when done
- **Export Fallback:** WebCodecs → MediaRecorder → api.video cloud transcoding

